To run this software, first install the dependencies (I recommend creating a python venv first):
    pip install -r requirements.txt
then run:
    python main.py
which will output usage information to the console.

An example linkage -- the Peaucellier-Lipkin linkage -- is
provided. To load it, use:
    python main.py peaucellier.txt

For more information, see:
    http://x.st/linkages/
